{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232660/extras/BibLogo.png?t=1737892830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Im Bann Der Dunklen Jagd</strong> invites you and a friend to an immersive co-op horror adventure, where you take on the role of detectives sent into a mysterious area. Your task is to gather clues and navigate through the eerie scenario. Experience the core gameplay of a level, where teamwork and careful exploration are essential to uncover the location's mystery and escape safely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232660/extras/Lupe.png?t=1737892830\" /><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cooperative Investigations:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is designed for two players. Work together to explore the area and find crucial objects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collecting Objects:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Search for clues and items scattered throughout the ominous environment. Your detective skills will be put to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232660/extras/Lupe.png?t=1737892830\" /><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Three Levels:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into three exciting levels where you work together to gather clues, solve puzzles, and successfully escape the area.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Threatening Atmosphere:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The scenario is characterized by a gloomy setting and eerie sounds that heighten the tension.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232660/extras/run.png?t=1737892830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Important Notes:</u></strong><br>This experience gives you a glimpse into the gameplay and core mechanics of <strong>Im Bann Der Dunklen Jagd</strong>. It\u2019s an early version of the game, offering a preview of what\u2019s to come. Your feedback is crucial and will help me further develop and improve the game.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"No Food, No Fight!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232660/a8571ca0047aac6e8d1f1ccf40bf460d6a8abb0e.jpg"},{"name":"ACT I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232660/8ced68346cd914811de45291f0c574cae947765f.jpg"},{"name":"ACT I COMPLETED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232660/dbe2e83ac7d52941bfd1998755da9100e243c192.jpg"},{"name":"Vital Mistake","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232660/ed007b89ab164ba1ddccf17249ddaf4f7c4c465b.jpg"},{"name":"New to the Game","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232660/52a000a1df5905888cdf6afb5f4fce60e7065839.jpg"},{"name":"Command Center","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232660/fb4e41f83450fc2dc31301154fb7c89adfbec1f5.jpg"},{"name":"ACT II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232660/54e225907bc67edb54e32fab2263adafb8f4f007.jpg"},{"name":"ACT II COMPLETED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232660/cef9decbe69dc59841afe8f73d6b056484393ab0.jpg"},{"name":"Keeper of Flames","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/